                Proyecto integrador, es una aplicación web (e-commerce) desarrollada para facilitar la digitalización de tiendas dietéticas físicas.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 md:gap-3 mt-4 md:mt-6">
                <SocialPill class="text-xs md:text-sm">
                    <HTMLIcon class="size-4 md:size-5" aria-label="HTML" />
                    <span class="sr-only">HTML</span>
                    HTML
                </SocialPill>
                <SocialPill class="text-xs md:text-sm">
                    <CSSIcon class="size-4 md:size-5" aria-label="CSS" />
                    <span class="sr-only">CSS</span>
                    CSS
                </SocialPill>
                <SocialPill class="text-xs md:text-sm">
                    <JavaScriptIcon class="size-4 md:size-5" aria-label="Javascript" />
                    <span class="sr-only">Javascript</span>
                    Javascript
                </SocialPill>
                <SocialPill class="text-xs md:text-sm">
                    <ReactIcon class="size-4 md:size-5" aria-label="React" />
                    <span class="sr-only">React</span>
                    React
                </SocialPill>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 md:gap-4 mt-4 md:mt-6">
                <a href="https://github.com/ceballosAgustin/proyecto-dietetic-shop" 
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="flex items-center gap-2 px-6 md:px-8 py-2 md:py-3 
                border border-light-grey/20 bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-gray-700/20 hover:scale-105"
                aria-label="Ver repositorio de Dietetic-Shop en GitHub (se abre en una ventana nueva)">   
                <GitHubIcon class="size-4 md:size-5" />
                    <span>Ver Repositorio</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-light-pink/20 
        hover:border-light-lavanda/40 transition-all group">
        <div class="w-full h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
